title: Dutch Investigators 'Sloughed Off' Cooperation With Russia on MH17 Crash
text: Russia has expressed its disappointment several times over the fact that the Dutch investigations on the cause of the downing of the MH17 airlines last year over eastern Ukraine have basically sloughed off cooperation with Russian specialists, Kremlin spokesman Dmitry Peskov said Monday. ...
